{
  "stem": "71.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I turned-- I came out, and I-- I saw a tank.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I recognized the Russian tank because I was in Poland on the Russian side, and I saw the tanks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I ran, and I jumped on the stoop, and the soldier grabbed me by the hand and pulled me up and gave me a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the meantime, half of the lager-- camp came out and threw me down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody was stepping-- how I came out alive from that, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But when my sister [INAUDIBLE] Regina unwrapped the loaf of bread, it had mold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they were so-- you know, they were gracious to give away-- they themselves did not have very much.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we stayed there for quite a while, and then we went.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Some other people came, and they brought in other people after from different camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it became a disaster there, because a lot, a lot of sick people came in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were dying every day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Somebody told us that a man that lived in the same building was there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So whatever little we had, I went-- and you couldn't go in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were guards because the typhoid was-- fever was raging.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So you couldn't go in there, but I climbed a window.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when I jumped in, I-- I fell on maybe 20 corpses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "When I-- I-- I went down to bring to that man-- they said the man is sick.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So whatever I had, I don't remember, a little soup or piece of bread or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he kissed me and hugged me, and he says, get out of here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because he knew that, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we stayed in Theresienstadt for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then we went on it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
